*.txt
*.pyc
# -------------------------------------------------
# 1. Ignore EVERYTHING by default
# -------------------------------------------------
*

# -------------------------------------------------
# 2. Un-ignore files & folders that start with A-Z
# -------------------------------------------------
![^A-Z]*
!/[A-Z]*/

# -------------------------------------------------
# 3. Re-include the contents of the kept folders
# -------------------------------------------------
[A-Z]*/**
!/[A-Z]*/**

# -------------------------------------------------
# 4. Keep the .gitignore itself (and any other dot-files you need)
# -------------------------------------------------
!.gitignore